title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 36] New Wave
description:
And four more gems from the best decade of music, ever. Seed and enjoy. Spread this great music which deserves to be heard and recognized, though quarter a century late. Happy new year to all of you and best wishes for the new year!  


Bruce Foxton - Touch Sensitive (1984)

Minor Detail - Minor Detail [1983]

Slow Children - Slow Children (1981)

Zaine Griff - Figures (1982)
